## SequenceInterval type

Sequence interval object based on gff3 field specs. Recursively defined: SequenceInterval children are SequenceIntervals themselves.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export type SequenceInterval = {
    ID: string;
    seqid: string;
    source: string;
    interval_type: string;
    start: number;
    end: number;
    score: number | string;
    strand: "+" | "-" | ".";
    phase: 0 | 1 | 2 | ".";
    attributes: Record<string, string[] | string>;
    children?: SequenceInterval[];
};
```
